Money systems can be better Ryan Taylor.title: Money systems can be better Ryan Taylor CEO of Dash Core Group
Money systems can be better Ryan Taylor.description: Bitsonline's George Levy interviewed Ryan Taylor, CEO of Dash Core Group at the 2018 Las Vegas Money 20/20 event. During the segment, Ryan presents his vision that money systems can be better. In the process, he explains Dash's participation in Money 20/20, their governance model and how Dash is actively working towards a vision for developing the future of money. Interviewer: George Levy Post-production: Tyson O'Ham

The future of Crypto Breaking new ground.title: The future of Crypto Breaking new ground in emerging markets
The future of Crypto Breaking new ground.description: Dash is breaking new ground in terms of widespread cryptocurrency adoption by providing unbanked and underbanked people with more financial options and better economic solutions. In this talk, Dash Core Group CEO Ryan Taylor explores some of the unique challenges of money systems with Anne Gaviola around the world and explains how cryptocurrencies can lubricate commerce and facilitate daily transactions.

CEO of Overstock thinks the Govt Should.description: CEO of Overstock, Patrick Byrne, talks with me at Porcfest about the financial system, and what he believes should be the government's role in bitcoin.
